🧮 Simple Calculator

A fully functional calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It performs basic arithmetic operations and includes features like delete and clear.

🚀 Features

Basic operations: `+`, `-`, `×`, `÷`, `%`
Delete (`DEL`) and Clear (`C`) functions
Responsive design
Interactive button-based UI

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML for structure
CSS for styling
JavaScript for logic and interactivity


▶️ How to Use

1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Open the "index.html" file in your browser.
3. Start calculating!

📂 Project Structure


calculator/
│
├── index.html        # Main HTML file
├── style.css         # Styling with CSS
├── script.js         # JavaScript logic
└── README.md         # This file


📌 Future Improvements

 Keyboard input support
 Dark/light mode toggle
 Calculation history
